OCEAN GROVE CAMP MEETING ASSOCIATION v. BOARD OF EDUCATION OF THE TOWNSHIP OF NEPTUNE. Submitted July 6, 1925 Decided August 21, 1925.

Before Justices Tren chard and Katzenbach.

For the applicant, Augustus G. Sluder, Jr. Per Curiam:

An application for a writ of certiorari having been denied by this court, a further application was made to mould the pleadings as set forth in the correspondence filed herewith.
